  <brief_title>Confirming The Sitaxsentan Dose In Patients Undergoing Heart Surgery</brief_title>
  <acronym>FCAD02</acronym>
  <official_title>Selective Endothelin Type A Receptor Inhibition In Cardiac Surgery Subjects With Pre-Existing Cardiovascular Risk Factors: A Dose Confirmation Study</official_title>
