  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multi-center, randomized study of sitaxsentan administered intravenously to
      subjects who are undergoing elective CABG, cardiac valve replacement, or combined CABG and
      cardiac valve replacement procedures that require CPB.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
